    "title": "Bubble.io: Build Full Web Apps Without Writing Code",
    "excerpt": "Bubble.io lets you build production-ready web apps with visual logic, databases, and UI — no coding needed. See why thousands trust it for SaaS and marketplaces.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/what-is-bubble.jpg",
