    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever had an app idea — a SaaS tool, a marketplace, an internal dashboard — and thought *\"I can't build that without a developer,\"* Bubble.io is about to change your mind.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bubble is a full-stack no-code platform that lets you design, build, and launch real web applications using a visual editor. We're not talking about landing pages or simple forms. Bubble handles complex logic, relational databases, user authentication, API integrations, and pixel-perfect UI — all without writing a single line of code.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "It's been around since 2012, and it's grown into one of the most respected names in the no-code space. Founders at Y Combinator use it. Agencies ship entire businesses on it. Solo entrepreneurs have built products with thousands of paying users using Bubble alone.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's break down exactly what Bubble is, what it does exceptionally well, and whether it's the right tool for your next project.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
