      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, Bubble is a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "visual development environment",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for web applications. Think of it as a blank canvas where you drag and drop elements — buttons, inputs, text, images, repeating groups — and then define workflows that tell the app what to do when users interact with those elements.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But here's what sets Bubble apart from simpler tools like Wix or Squarespace: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "it's genuinely full-stack.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
