          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Many no-code platforms give you beautiful templates but fall apart the moment you need conditional logic, multi-step workflows, or backend processing. Bubble doesn't have this limitation.",
