      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bubble's visual editor gives you genuine design control. You're not locked into rigid templates. You can position elements with absolute precision, control responsive behavior across screen sizes, use custom CSS classes, and create animations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform has steadily improved its design tools. Recent updates include a ",
