            "text": "Bubble runs on AWS infrastructure. Apps hosted on Bubble benefit from automatic scaling, SSL certificates, and CDN distribution. For most startups and growing businesses, this means you don't need to worry about DevOps, server management, or infrastructure costs until you're already generating revenue.",
