    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/bubble.io as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A person sitting at a modern desk with dual monitors showing a colorful drag-and-drop app builder interface, hands on keyboard, natural daylight from a window, minimalist office. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Bubble.io really free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Bubble's free plan gives you full access to the visual editor, database, and workflow engine. You can build and test your entire app without paying. The free plan includes Bubble branding and a Bubble subdomain. When you're ready to launch publicly with a custom domain, plans start at $29/month.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Bubble handle complex applications like marketplaces or SaaS platforms?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Bubble supports relational databases, conditional workflows, API integrations, and role-based user permissions — all the building blocks needed for marketplaces, SaaS dashboards, booking platforms, and more. Thousands of production apps handling real transactions run on Bubble today.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need any coding experience to use Bubble?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No coding experience is required. Bubble uses a visual drag-and-drop interface for design and a visual workflow editor for logic. That said, thinking logically — understanding if/then conditions and data relationships — helps significantly. Many successful Bubble builders started with zero technical background.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Bubble compare to hiring a developer?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For many web application projects, Bubble lets you build 5-10x faster and at a fraction of the cost of traditional development. You maintain full control to iterate without developer dependencies. It's not a fit for every project (native mobile games, for example), but for web-based SaaS tools, marketplaces, and internal apps, it's remarkably competitive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
